Privacy Policy

Welcome to "Passport Photo Maker - Greencard". Safeguarding your privacy and personal information is our priority. By using the App, you acknowledge and consent to the provisions outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect and Third-Party Frameworks
In-App Purchases:
To facilitate smooth in-app transactions, we gather essential payment details such as credit card information, ensuring secure processing.

Usage Information:
We collect statistical data, including usage frequency and page views, to enhance app performance and optimize user experience.

Cookies:
Our app may utilize cookies or similar tracking technologies to enhance user experience and improve app functionality. These technologies may collect information such as device identifiers, IP addresses, and browsing history. You can disable cookies in your device settings, but note that it may affect certain app features.

Children's Privacy:
We do not knowingly collect personal information from users under the age of 4. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information without parental consent, please contact us at infoappnine@gmail.com and we will promptly remove such information from our records.

Third-Party Frameworks:
We utilize third-party frameworks, such as Reusable and RevenueCat, for app analytics, functionality enhancement, and in-app purchases. Please refer to their respective privacy policies for more information:

Reusable Privacy Policy
RevenueCat Privacy Policy
Data Sharing and Security of Personal Data:
We may share payment-related information with third-party payment service providers solely for secure transaction processing. Stringent security measures are in place to protect sensitive data, including payment information, from unauthorized access.

Changes to the Privacy Policy:
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

This policy is effective as of 2023-08-01.

Contact:
For queries regarding our privacy practices, kindly reach out to us at omercaslan@gmail.com.
